</m:math>, since the charges move an average distance <m:math><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:math> in a time <m:math><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>Δ</m:mn><m:mi fontstyle="italic">t</m:mi></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:math>. Rearranging terms gives</para><equation id="eip-733"><m:math>
        
